---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Products
description: Browse Acme Chemicals' comprehensive portfolio of industrial solvents, specialty polymers, surfactants, water treatment chemicals, and adhesives.
permalink: /products/
---

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span>Products</span>
    </div>
    <h1>Our Product Portfolio</h1>
    <p class="lead">High-performance chemicals engineered for precision, reliability, and compliance across the world's most demanding industries.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card-grid">
      {% for product in collections.products | reverse %}
      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="{{ product.data.image }}" alt="{{ product.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-tag">{{ product.data.category }}</span>
          <h3>{{ product.data.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ product.data.excerpt }}</p>
          <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="card-link">View Product Details</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="overline">Quality Assurance</span>
      <h2>Every product. Every batch. Every time.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">🏭</div>
        <h3>GMP Manufacturing</h3>
        <p>All products are manufactured under Good Manufacturing Practices with full traceability from raw material to finished good.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">📋</div>
        <h3>Full Documentation</h3>
        <p>Certificates of Analysis, Safety Data Sheets, and technical datasheets available for every product, every batch.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">🧪</div>
        <h3>In-House Testing</h3>
        <p>Our accredited laboratories perform over 600 individual quality checks before any product leaves our facilities.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <div class="feature-icon">🌍</div>
        <h3>Global Compliance</h3>
        <p>Full compliance with REACH, RoHS, FDA, and regional chemical regulations in all 80+ markets we serve.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Need a custom formulation?</h2>
    <p>Our R&D team can develop tailored chemical solutions to meet your specific performance, regulatory, and sustainability requirements.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Talk to a Chemist</a>
      <a href="/safety/" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">Download SDS Sheets</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
